  coach_language = 'Primary subrole: jump/throw explosive power. Coach Squat Jump to Stick for jump-height transfer: Jump straight up, land where you started, and stick clean. Keep the dose small enough that every rep preserves speed, posture, contact quality, and pain-free control.',
